<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Delicious Food</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="page.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Welcome to Delicious Food</h1>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#home">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                <li><a href="#menu">Menu</a></li>
                <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section id="home">
        <h2>Home</h2>
        <p>Welcome to our food website where you can find the most delicious recipes and dishes!</p>
    </section>

    <section id="about">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>We are passionate about food and sharing our love of cooking with you. Our goal is to bring you the best recipes and cooking tips.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="menu">
        <h2>Our Menu</h2>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Spaghetti Carbonara</h3>
            <p>A classic Italian pasta dish made with eggs, cheese, pancetta, and pepper.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Margherita Pizza</h3>
            <p>A simple yet delicious pizza topped with fresh tomatoes, mozzarella, and basil.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="menu-item">
            <h3>Caesar Salad</h3>
            <p>Crisp romaine lettuce tossed with Caesar dressing, croutons, and Parmesan cheese.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>Have any questions or feedback? Feel free to reach out to us!</p>
        <form>
            <label for="name">Name:</label>
            <input type="text" id="name" name="name">
            <label for="email">Email:</label>
            <input type="email" id="email" name="email">
            <label for="message">Message:</label>
            <textarea id="message" name="message"></textarea>
            <button type="submit">Submit</button>
        </form>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 Delicious Food. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
